{"tid":437350,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真正鐘意足球嘅人是不會反哥帥的。","createTime":"2017-10-16T02:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T15:56:09.000Z","uid":59491,"like":20,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2b75d677d1d04df72d18a00c43c7838d0f64478e","tid":437350,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:36:37.000Z","msg":"根本哥帥呢個人專們為足球而設咁<br />\n巴塞青訓+告魯夫弟子<br />\n正正係佢成功既主要因素之一<br />\n全攻全守,靈活走位<br />\n睇佢教波真係會睇到 ''嘩''一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為你知佢點踢都守唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得足球真係欠哥帥一個英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相反有個廢柴剩係識洗錢泊大巴<br />\n屌球證<br />\n弱隊泊巴士就屌鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261fd2a1af7f24873fff290ec0e0429c9f355ecd","tid":437350,"uid":4957,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"因住比狗咬"},{"pid":"1df5291cd55890420a4a8a8af5b917873ef09796","tid":437350,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"佢離開巴塞同拜仁之後 呢兩隊波即刻冇晒係聯賽嘅統治力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a2e742a99d6209a9b5544dde2f899fa727ed73","tid":437350,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"我後悔反哥了"},{"pid":"d8afc566d74d7c43ba5173d09720d29bf5784445","tid":437350,"uid":27907,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:47:26.000Z","msg":"哥帥勁係事實<br />\n都唔洗借啲依踩其他人既 <br />\n成個post低質哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511cc11e680140b0acb2ccc232f49bfe2aea860e","tid":437350,"uid":59491,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"<